<div>
    <h2>
        <span class="helpWidget" data-help-content-id="help-description-content"
            data-show-text="show help" data-hide-text="hide help">
        </span>
        <label for="dc:description">Description</label>
    </h2>
    <div id="help-description-content" class="help-content">
        <p>Description of the research that generated the dataset.</p>
        This should include:
        <ul>
            <li>information about the project</li>
            <li>the purpose and scope of the data</li>
            <li>entities being studied or recorded</li>
            <li>methodology</li>
            <li>characteristics and features of the data</li>
        </ul>
##        <p>The description could include:</p>
